text: The National Library of Indonesia is in Jakarta, the capital city of Indonesia. It is the country's national library. It was started on 17 May 1980. By law, a copy of all printed works published in Indonesia must be given to the National Library. == Surreal == == Other websites == *Official website Category:National libraries in Asia Category:Buildings and structures in Jakarta Category:1980 establishments in Asia Category:1980s establishments in Indonesia
